    Section 2 **collective employment contract**: repealed, on 2 October 2000, by [section 240][205] of the Employment Relations Act 2000 (2000 No 24).
    
    Section 2 **college of education**: repealed, on 25 January 2005, by [section 17(a)][206] of the State Sector Amendment Act (No 2) 2004 (2004 No 114).
    
    Section 2 **Crown entity**: inserted, on 25 January 2005, by [section 4(2)][204] of the State Sector Amendment Act (No 2) 2004 (2004 No 114).
    
    Section 2 **Crown Research Institute**: inserted, on 25 January 2005, by [section 4(2)][204] of the State Sector Amendment Act (No 2) 2004 (2004 No 114).
    
